                            <comment id="13959814" author="alex.parvulescu" created="Fri, 4 Apr 2014 09:35:03 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;fyi Angela, I&apos;ve changed the fix version to 1.1, as the 0.20 has already been cut, but due to some infra issues the release is not out yet.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
